England Batsman Eoin Morgan to Undergo Surgery on Right Shoulder

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-09-09T14:18:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-09/england-batsman-eoin-morgan-to-undergo-surgery-on-right-shoulder.html
England  batsman Eoin Morgan will
undergo sugery on his right shoulder next week, the England and
Wales Cricket Board said in a statement.  Morgan will sidelined for 12 weeks, keeping him out of the
one-day international series in  India  next month. He’s expected
to be fully fit for England’s tour of the United Arab Emirates
beginning in January, the England board said.  Morgan was ruled out of the final four games of England’s
current one-day home series against India three days ago because
of the injury.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  